{
  "stem": "12289.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So it's a balance that whole time, which is very cruel that you-- you had to say, denied, to some.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I'm sorry, we can't give you a passport.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had-- you had to prove that you have relatives in Sweden, you have that and that and that.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So you had to, at least officially, be very restrictive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You had to build up a bureaucracy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That was our-- our weapon, in a way, against the Germans, to show them, look here, we-- we are doing everything legally here.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We have these criteria.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "People who give-- get this passport have to have Swedish relationship and so on and so on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We have officers, here, all sitting and-- and scrutinizing all the backgrounds of all these people and all.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Very thorough work, you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we can show you all the dossier and all that and so on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was how it-- how it went, you see?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Which didn't prevent, of course, Wallenberg, towards the very end, when everything was falling in pieces, to give away passports like that.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was the last weeks before the-- the Russians came.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What kind of problem did you get with the Germans?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What kind of a--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With the Germans?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, we didn't have-- The problems were, of course, that-- that was the negotiations between Wallenberg and Eichmann.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That when he tried to get Eichmann to understand, that he must now understand, that you are losing the war and all that, and that you would-- it would be to your advantage to show some-- give some liberty here to the Jews, not to-- to go on along the same lines as you-- You could perhaps save your own life.",
      "word_count": 61
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But he'd never listen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He never listened to that.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
